@theodysseymovie press tour is officially underway. After kicking off with a photocall along the River Thames on 6 July, the star-studded cast, including @zendaya, Tom Holland, @annehathaway, Lupita Nyong’o, Robert Pattinson and Matt Damon, brought the drama to the London premiere with a red carpet full of standout fashion moments.
From #AnneHathaway’s silk @Dior gown to #MiaGoth’s embroidered #Dior dress, the cast embraced the film’s epic spirit through sculptural silhouettes, Grecian-inspired draping and impeccable tailoring.
At the link in bio, every standout look from The Odyssey press tour so far.

The countdown has officially begun.
In less than 24 hours, Manish Malhotra will make his highly anticipated debut at Paris Haute Couture Week, marking a defining moment not only in his career but also for Indian couture on one of fashion's most prestigious global stages. Set against the historic backdrop of the Pavillon Cambon, the showcase is expected to celebrate the designer's signature craftsmanship, intricate embroidery and contemporary vision, while also unveiling exceptional creations from Manish Malhotra High Jewellery.
With much of the collection still under wraps, anticipation continues to build as the fashion world waits to see what unfolds in Paris tomorrow.
